Usage: get_lib_pins [-help] [-filter <expr>] [-nocase] [-quiet] [-regexp] { <pattern_list> | -of_objects <object_list> }

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<pattern_list>                # Returns only those libraries in the collection
                              # whose name matches one or more of the patterns
                              # specified in the pattern_list argument
                              # (string, optional)
-filter <expr>                # Filters the collection with the specified
                              # expression (string, optional)
-nocase                       # Pattern matching is not case sensitive
                              # (bool, optional)
-of_objects <object_list>     # Creates a collection of all library pins
                              # associated with the specified library cells or
                              # pins (string, optional)
-quiet                        # Suppresses all error and warning messages
                              # generated when the get_lib_pins command is run
                              # (bool, optional)
-regexp                       # Treats the specified patterns as a regular
                              # expression patterns (bool, optional)